1. *Uvek* se trudim da budem iskren. (I always try to be honest.)
2. Ona *uvek* izgleda tako lepo. (She always looks so pretty.)
3. Danas mi je bio težak dan, ali *uvek* se trudim da ostanem pozitivan. (Today was a hard day for me, but I always try to stay positive.)
4. *Uvek* ću se vratiti kući. (I will always come back home.)
5. *Uvek* ću biti tu za tebe. (I will always be there for you.)